No, the works are the manifestation of his faith.

656
00:52:41,539 --> 00:52:44,539
So verse 24, you see then how that by works, amen,

657
00:52:44,539 --> 00:52:46,819
is justified and not by faith only.

658
00:52:46,819 --> 00:52:49,499
Again, let me say this in closing this morning.

659
00:52:49,499 --> 00:52:51,819
Instead of dismissing the text of scripture

660
00:52:51,819 --> 00:52:53,819
due to an apparent contradiction

661
00:52:53,819 --> 00:52:56,459
or due to some denomination using the text

662
00:52:56,859 --> 00:52:57,899
to teach false doctrine,

663
00:52:57,899 --> 00:53:01,359
what we really should do is examine our lives

664
00:53:01,359 --> 00:53:05,219
to see if our faith is evident to others

665
00:53:05,219 --> 00:53:06,359
through our behavior.

666
00:53:09,059 --> 00:53:12,719
It's easy to dismiss scripture for some.

667
00:53:12,719 --> 00:53:14,419
No, we shouldn't.

668
00:53:14,419 --> 00:53:15,819
But when there's an apparent contradiction

669
00:53:15,819 --> 00:53:18,279
or maybe there's a denomination that teaches something false

670
00:53:18,279 --> 00:53:19,639
about a portion of scripture,

671
00:53:19,639 --> 00:53:20,479
if we're not careful and say,

672
00:53:20,479 --> 00:53:21,379
well, we're just not gonna,

673
00:53:21,379 --> 00:53:23,679
we're gonna kind of dismiss, no, no, no.

674
00:53:23,679 --> 00:53:25,479
Every word of God is pure.

675
00:53:25,479 --> 00:53:26,919
And it's there for a reason.

676
00:53:26,919 --> 00:53:28,199
And I'm not gonna dismiss it.

677
00:53:28,199 --> 00:53:29,319
I'm not gonna excuse it.

678
00:53:29,319 --> 00:53:31,519
I'm not gonna say, well, some denomination

679
00:53:31,519 --> 00:53:33,439
corrupted this portion of scripture

680
00:53:33,439 --> 00:53:34,639
and therefore I'm not gonna follow.

681
00:53:34,639 --> 00:53:35,479
No, no, no.

682
00:53:36,479 --> 00:53:38,919
Listen, the Pentecostals have messed up

683
00:53:38,919 --> 00:53:40,199
with the whole Holy Spirit thing,

684
00:53:40,199 --> 00:53:41,319
but it doesn't mean that we don't believe

685
00:53:41,319 --> 00:53:42,919
that the Holy Spirit and that I'm supposed to be filled

686
00:53:42,919 --> 00:53:45,599
with the Holy Spirit, amen?

687
00:53:45,599 --> 00:53:48,279
Yeah, no, no, you're not supposed to be speaking in tongues

688
00:53:48,279 --> 00:53:49,979
and all that kind of nonsense.

689
00:53:49,979 --> 00:53:52,319
But we understand that there is a Holy Spirit

690
00:53:52,319 --> 00:53:53,759
and he is part of the Trinity

691
00:53:53,759 --> 00:53:56,459
and he does indwell us at the time of salvation

692
00:53:56,459 --> 00:53:58,399
and we are to be filled with the Holy Spirit

693
00:53:58,399 --> 00:53:59,899
and I am to walk in the Spirit

694
00:53:59,899 --> 00:54:01,799
so that I do not fulfill the lust of the flesh.

695
00:54:01,799 --> 00:54:02,719
Hallelujah.

696
00:54:02,719 --> 00:54:04,999
I'm not gonna skip teaching on the Holy Spirit of God

697
00:54:04,999 --> 00:54:08,539
because of some denominational group that's corrupted it.

698
00:54:08,539 --> 00:54:09,919
Does it make sense?

699
00:54:09,919 --> 00:54:13,219
So the same is true in James chapter number two.

700
00:54:13,219 --> 00:54:14,319
There's no contradiction.

701
00:54:14,319 --> 00:54:17,559
Well, it says that Abraham was justified by works.

702
00:54:18,419 --> 00:54:21,839
Understand the events, understand the emphasis,

703
00:54:22,239 --> 00:54:24,699
and then evaluate your own life.

704
00:54:25,679 --> 00:54:30,679
What work in my life, what in my behavior

705
00:54:31,199 --> 00:54:36,199
is the evidence to those around me that I believe God?

706
00:54:36,319 --> 00:54:40,039
Remember, I said this on Wednesday, thinking about Noah.

707
00:54:42,479 --> 00:54:43,919
That ark is huge.

708
00:54:46,759 --> 00:54:48,859
He couldn't build that thing undercover.

709
00:54:49,019 --> 00:54:49,859
He couldn't.

710
00:54:51,019 --> 00:54:51,859
Amen?

711
00:54:53,099 --> 00:54:56,939
Everybody around knew that Noah was building an ark.

712
00:54:56,939 --> 00:54:58,339
There was no way to hide it.

713
00:54:59,259 --> 00:55:01,019
I asked this both in the morning session

714
00:55:01,019 --> 00:55:02,459
and the evening session on Wednesday,

715
00:55:02,459 --> 00:55:03,339
who's been to the ark?

716
00:55:03,339 --> 00:55:05,399
I've been there, out in Kentucky.

717
00:55:06,619 --> 00:55:08,019
Listen, you come around the corner,

718
00:55:08,019 --> 00:55:09,599
you're not gonna miss it.

719
00:55:09,599 --> 00:55:12,339
You have to be absolutely blind to miss it.

720
00:55:12,339 --> 00:55:13,439
It's huge.

721
00:55:17,379 --> 00:55:18,619
What are you doing, Noah?

722
00:55:19,859 --> 00:55:21,139
Well, God told me it was gonna rain

723
00:55:21,139 --> 00:55:22,539
and he's gonna destroy it with flood,

724
00:55:22,539 --> 00:55:24,499
and he told me to build this ark.

725
00:55:24,499 --> 00:55:26,299
What's rain, Noah?

726
00:55:26,299 --> 00:55:28,179
What's a flood, Noah?

727
00:55:28,179 --> 00:55:29,539
What's an ark, Noah?

728
00:55:30,499 --> 00:55:32,179
I don't know, but God told me to do it,

729
00:55:32,179 --> 00:55:34,739
and I'm gonna do it because I believe God.

730
00:55:35,939 --> 00:55:38,739
Though you might be mocked, ridiculed,

731
00:55:38,739 --> 00:55:41,379
made fun of, whatever it might be,

732
00:55:41,379 --> 00:55:46,219
my faith is evidenced through my behavior.

733
00:55:46,499 --> 00:55:49,419
And that's the emphasis that James is seeking

734
00:55:49,419 --> 00:55:53,499
to drive home for these believers.

735
00:55:53,499 --> 00:55:56,819
And so this morning, we must evaluate our lives.

736
00:55:56,819 --> 00:55:59,019
What does my behavior say about my faith?

737
00:56:00,339 --> 00:56:01,899
Would others see my behavior and say,

738
00:56:01,899 --> 00:56:04,159
man, they believe God?

739
00:56:04,159 --> 00:56:06,179
I hope it would be the case.

740
00:56:06,179 --> 00:56:07,019
Let's pray.

741
00:56:07,019 --> 00:56:08,419
Father, we love you.

742
00:56:08,419 --> 00:56:09,499
Thank you for loving us.

743
00:56:09,499 --> 00:56:11,659
Thank you for the word of God.

744
00:56:11,659 --> 00:56:14,499
Maybe this morning someone's here that's not saved.

745
00:56:15,459 --> 00:56:16,579
Lord, they need to be saved.

746
00:56:16,579 --> 00:56:17,939
They need to be born again.

747
00:56:19,139 --> 00:56:21,699
I pray in these quiet moments of invitation

748
00:56:21,699 --> 00:56:23,619
that they'd come and allow us to take a Bible

749
00:56:23,619 --> 00:56:25,659
and they'd place their faith and trust

750
00:56:25,659 --> 00:56:27,779
in the finished work of Christ at Calvary.

751
00:56:30,379 --> 00:56:33,459
Maybe this morning, though, there's some people of God,

752
00:56:33,459 --> 00:56:36,059
some that have been born again, saved,

753
00:56:36,059 --> 00:56:38,379
that aren't really living by faith.

754
00:56:39,859 --> 00:56:41,299
They're not living by faith.

755
00:56:41,459 --> 00:56:42,979
If they were asked, they would say

756
00:56:42,979 --> 00:56:44,699
that they believe all the right things,

757
00:56:44,699 --> 00:56:49,099
but their behavior doesn't really support what they say.

758
00:56:51,699 --> 00:56:55,539
Their prayer life doesn't reveal that they believe

759
00:56:55,539 --> 00:56:57,259
that you're a God who hears and answers,

760
00:56:57,259 --> 00:56:58,739
that's able to do exceeding abundantly

761
00:56:58,739 --> 00:57:00,379
above all that we ask or think.

762
00:57:03,579 --> 00:57:07,459
God, I pray that as we would evaluate our lives

763
00:57:07,459 --> 00:57:09,419
after examining the portion of scripture

764
00:57:09,699 --> 00:57:12,699
after examining the portion of scripture,

765
00:57:12,699 --> 00:57:14,219
that you would help each and every one of us

766
00:57:14,219 --> 00:57:16,419
to live by faith.

767
00:57:17,539 --> 00:57:19,099
I pray that each decision that's made

768
00:57:19,099 --> 00:57:21,259
would bring honor and glory to thy name.

769
00:57:21,259 --> 00:57:23,179
For it's in Christ's name we pray.

770
00:57:23,179 --> 00:57:24,059
Would you stand with me?

771
00:57:24,059 --> 00:57:25,659
Heads are bowed, eyes are closed.

772
00:57:27,579 --> 00:57:29,419
At the end of our services, we have an invitation.

773
00:57:29,419 --> 00:57:32,299
It's just an opportunity for you to respond.

774
00:57:32,299 --> 00:57:34,499
God spoke to you through his word this morning.

775
00:57:34,499 --> 00:57:36,099
Maybe you're not sure of heaven.

